<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="25Oct1940"><font color="red">25 October 1940</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Paul Ruggiero): The French authorities have granted us exit permits and we plan to leave tomorrow if we have the Swiss entry visas. My lawyer is M. Georges Haldenwang, 6 rue du Rh&ocirc;ne at Geneva </div>
